column23: This dataset is not the latest version and is made available to the humanitarian community for operational use only. Updated administrative boundaries are available for purchase from the Afghan Geodesy and Cartography Head Office (AGCHO) Afghanistan. Humanitarian responders in Afghanistan can collect a copy of latest available datasets from OCHA Afghanistan as a member of the Information Management Working Group (IMWG).
